<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="light dark" lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>CodeWave - Coding Quizzes</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<script id="tailwind-config">tailwind.config = {darkMode: "class", theme: {extend: {colors: {primary: "#9d64cf", "background-light": "#f7f6f8", "background-dark": "#19141e"}, fontFamily: {display: "Inter"}, borderRadius: {DEFAULT: "0.25rem", lg: "0.5rem", xl: "0.75rem", full: "9999px"}}}};</script>
<style>.code-syntax-keyword {
    color: #d73a49
    }
.code-syntax-string {
    color: #032f62
    }
.code-syntax-function {
    color: #6f42c1
    }
.code-syntax-number {
    color: #005cc5
    }
.form-radio:checked {
    background-image: url(https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBMVHLjrGP_M9labWnHKDHNq26LtiCaIWfGw__WSTWgMadnrbWi1LUJxzMJjLc5KU7sQLjqyn8tO007xGhe-QhdBuoX4lgqrKvzbS0LmH-PS9wZeWRzBonEFU_SH6f_7tZ5IRBM0_TZcKzK7H6Ey2it-31QzImnBW-Y0FeSaEkmrrPyfUIKowkD8PZzFliGHz7OKsAi_4JAyMyE7AAT09jMpmES7WgsdDsRI2kaOnMk5ULnB06xHWUKRxTybRgCOP4_cMaZ_iepUjY);
    border-color: transparent;
    background-color: currentColor;
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat
    }</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display text-[#151118] dark:text-white transition-colors duration-200">

<!-- Main Content Layout -->
<main class="flex min-h-[calc(100vh-73px)] flex-col items-center py-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="w-full max-w-5xl space-y-8">
<!-- Breadcrumbs -->
<nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-sm text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400">
<a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/Home">Courses</a>
<span class="mx-2 text-gray-400">/</span>
<a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/LearningPath/Course?courseId=22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222">Python Basics</a>
<span class="mx-2 text-gray-400">/</span>
<span class="font-medium text-[#151118] dark:text-white">List Comprehensions</span>
</nav>
<!-- Quiz Header & Progress -->
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1e1427] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-gray-800">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
<div>
<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#151118] dark:text-white">Python Logic Challenge</h1>
<p class="text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">Master list comprehensions and loops.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 bg-background-light dark:bg-[#2a2035] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">timer</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">14:20</span>
</div>
<button class="text-sm font-medium text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5">
                            Quit Quiz
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Progress Bar Component -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<div class="flex justify-between items-end">
<span class="text-primary font-bold text-sm">Question 3 of 10</span>
<span class="text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 text-xs font-medium">30% Completed</span>
</div>
<div class="h-2.5 w-full bg-[#f2f0f4] dark:bg-[#2a2035] rounded-full overflow-hidden">
<div class="h-full bg-primary rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out" style="width: 30%"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Two Column Layout for Question -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
<!-- Left Column: Problem Statement & Code -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
<!-- Question Card -->
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1e1427] rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-gray-800 overflow-hidden h-full flex flex-col">
<div class="p-6 border-b border-[#f2f0f4] dark:border-gray-800 bg-background-light/50 dark:bg-[#251b2e]">
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#151118] dark:text-white leading-tight">
                                What is the output of the following code snippet?
                            </h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                                Analyze the list comprehension logic carefully.
                            </p>
</div>
<!-- Code Snippet Display -->
<div class="p-6 bg-[#282c34] dark:bg-[#0d0912] flex-grow font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto">
<pre><code class="language-python block text-[#abb2bf]"><span class="text-[#c678dd]">numbers</span> = [<span class="text-[#d19a66]">1</span>, <span class="text-[#d19a66]">2</span>, <span class="text-[#d19a66]">3</span>]
<span class="text-[#776189] italic"># Create a new list with squares</span>
<span class="text-[#e06c75]">squares</span> = [n**<span class="text-[#d19a66]">2</span> <span class="text-[#c678dd]">for</span> n <span class="text-[#c678dd]">in</span> numbers]

<span class="text-[#e5c07b]">print</span>(squares)</code></pre>
</div>
<!-- Hint Section -->
<div class="p-4 bg-primary/5 dark:bg-primary/10 border-t border-primary/10 flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mt-0.5">lightbulb</span>
<div>
<p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Need a hint?</p>
<p class="text-xs text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">Remember that <code class="bg-white dark:bg-[#2a2035] px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-primary">**</code> is the exponentiation operator in Python.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right Column: Interactive Answers -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1e1427] rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-gray-800 p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
<div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
<h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#151118] dark:text-white">Select your answer</h4>
<span class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded uppercase tracking-wide">Single Choice</span>
</div>
<!-- Options List -->
<div class="space-y-3">
<!-- Option 1 -->
<label class="group relative flex items-center p-4 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#2a2035] cursor-pointer hover:border-primary/50 dark:hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-primary/5 dark:hover:bg-primary/10 transition-all duration-200">
<input class="size-5 text-primary border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 focus:ring-primary dark:focus:ring-offset-[#1e1427]" name="quiz-answer" type="radio" value="A"/>
<span class="ml-3 flex-1 font-mono text-sm text-[#151118] dark:text-gray-200">[1, 4, 9]</span>
<span class="absolute right-4 hidden group-hover:block text-primary text-xs font-medium">Select</span>
</label>
<!-- Option 2 -->
<label class="group relative flex items-center p-4 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#2a2035] cursor-pointer hover:border-primary/50 dark:hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-primary/5 dark:hover:bg-primary/10 transition-all duration-200">
<input class="size-5 text-primary border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 focus:ring-primary dark:focus:ring-offset-[#1e1427]" name="quiz-answer" type="radio" value="B"/>
<span class="ml-3 flex-1 font-mono text-sm text-[#151118] dark:text-gray-200">[1, 2, 3]</span>
</label>
<!-- Option 3 -->
<label class="group relative flex items-center p-4 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#2a2035] cursor-pointer hover:border-primary/50 dark:hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-primary/5 dark:hover:bg-primary/10 transition-all duration-200">
<input class="size-5 text-primary border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 focus:ring-primary dark:focus:ring-offset-[#1e1427]" name="quiz-answer" type="radio" value="C"/>
<span class="ml-3 flex-1 font-mono text-sm text-[#151118] dark:text-gray-200">Syntax Error</span>
</label>
<!-- Option 4 -->
<label class="group relative flex items-center p-4 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#2a2035] cursor-pointer hover:border-primary/50 dark:hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-primary/5 dark:hover:bg-primary/10 transition-all duration-200">
<input class="size-5 text-primary border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 focus:ring-primary dark:focus:ring-offset-[#1e1427]" name="quiz-answer" type="radio" value="D"/>
<span class="ml-3 flex-1 font-mono text-sm text-[#151118] dark:text-gray-200">[1, 4, 6]</span>
</label>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Action Buttons -->
<div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[#f2f0f4] dark:border-gray-800 flex items-center justify-between">
<button class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-[#f2f0f4] dark:hover:bg-[#2a2035] transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_back</span>
                                Previous
                            </button>
<div class="flex gap-3">
<button class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-[#151118] dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                    Skip
                                </button>
<button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white px-8 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 transition-all active:scale-95 flex items-center gap-2">
                                    Submit
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">check</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Additional Learning Resource / Footer Context -->
<div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[#776189] dark:text-gray-500 bg-white dark:bg-[#1e1427] px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-gray-800">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">school</span>
<span>This question is from the <a class="text-primary hover:underline" href="/LearningPath/Course?courseId=22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222">Python Intermediate Course</a></span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</body>
</html>